Package com.nkoiv.mists.game.ui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UIComponent
    UIComponent is the interface for anything drawn on the UI layer Everything visible on the UI should implement this.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionButton
    ActionButtons (currently) extend the Test button, with the addition of being mapped to an action of a player.
    AudioControls
    AudioControls contains the button elements for controlling the SoundManager (Music and Soundeffects).
    AudioControls.MuteMusicButton  
    GoMainMenuButton  
    MainMenuWindow
    MainMenuWindow is the actual Main Menu displayed by the MainMenuState.
    QuitButton
    QuitButton extends the TextButton, and simply calls Platform.exit() and System.exit(0) when clicked, closing the game.
    TextButton
    TextButton is a simple UI component with only a box and a text.
    TiledWindow
    Window is the basic UI component.
